Gonna try the POP

NO Password Required (when I extracted POP RS).
POP Revelations (NOT Rival Swords) worked nice until the Intro, where it shuts down (hard Shut Down) my PSP.
I have a PSP3000 with LCFW 6.60 ME-1.5.

It seems the problem in the intro was caused by applying compression (".cso").
after trying with the normal ".iso" file it worked fine.
Thanks VM! Keep up the good work.
